60
00:05:45.111 --> 00:05:48.047
Shannon: If he got shot.

61
00:05:48.081 --> 00:05:50.482
Elliot: We will find
out who's doing this.

62
00:05:54.421 --> 00:05:59.052
As for Danny. he'll be fine.

63
00:05:59.092 --> 00:06:02.085
He's tough. Shannon: Yeah.

64
00:06:02.128 --> 00:06:04.723
Elliot: He's watching "Marcus
And His Magical Boots."

65
00:06:04.764 --> 00:06:06.790
Shannon: Yeah. That's that.

66
00:06:12.739 --> 00:06:14.537
Elliot: Samuel used to watch it.

67
00:06:18.478 --> 00:06:21.107
Shannon: I love that you
can talk about him with me.

68
00:06:26.920 --> 00:06:30.084
Elliot: Me. too.

69
00:06:30.123 --> 00:06:32.524
[Banging]

70
00:06:32.559 --> 00:06:34.926
Shannon: Shit. Elliot:
Danny? Shannon: Danny?

71
00:06:34.961 --> 00:06:36.691
Danny?

72
00:06:36.730 --> 00:06:38.028
Danny!

73
00:06:38.064 --> 00:06:41.660
You alright. Yeah?

74
00:06:41.701 --> 00:06:42.862
Good boy.

75
00:06:49.476 --> 00:06:51.445
Fucking hell!

76
00:06:51.478 --> 00:06:53.674
It's fine. It's fine.

77
00:06:53.713 --> 00:06:55.113
Elliot: Are you okay. kid?

78
00:06:55.148 --> 00:06:56.582
You sure. yeah?

79
00:07:01.588 --> 00:07:02.765
