to be watching the house.

80
00:07:02.789 --> 00:07:03.552
not on your fucking phone!

81
00:07:03.590 --> 00:07:07.789
[Indistinct talking]

82
00:07:07.827 --> 00:07:09.125
Fucking do your job!

83
00:07:32.619 --> 00:07:33.619
Man: Excellent.

84
00:07:36.756 --> 00:07:39.191
Yes. very good.

85
00:07:39.225 --> 00:07:41.194
Luan: When does
our money come in?

86
00:07:41.227 --> 00:07:45.028
Man: Tomorrow. once Alex Dumani
has overseen the transfer of funds.

87
00:07:45.065 --> 00:07:46.065
Zeus. come.

88
00:07:46.766 --> 00:07:53.104
Ed? Please thank Sean
for honoring his father's deal.

89
00:07:53.139 --> 00:07:55.734
particularly in such
confusing times.

90
00:07:55.775 --> 00:07:59.610
