93
00:08:06.886 --> 00:08:09.014
The family that
Finn wanted to...

94
00:08:09.055 --> 00:08:13.584
to get rid of made their
money in oil and storage.

95
00:08:17.197 --> 00:08:21.760
Ed: You did this favor for
Finn. we washed your money...

96
00:08:21.801 --> 00:08:24.862
Or should I say Mosi's money?

97
00:08:27.207 --> 00:08:30.143
What. you thought
we wouldn't find out?

98
00:08:30.176 --> 00:08:33.010
You're building a tower for him.

99
00:08:33.046 --> 00:08:34.981
This is your free pass. Luan.

100
00:08:35.015 --> 00:08:40.511
You get to build one
tower in this city... one.

101
00:08:40.553 --> 00:08:43.216
But do not think you
get to go against us.

102
00:08:43.256 --> 00:08:46.693
And careful... Mosi
as a business partner

103
00:08:46.726 --> 00:08:49.252
