121
00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:14.907
We need that.

122
00:10:14.948 --> 00:10:16.211
Ed: Are you three okay?

123
00:10:16.249 --> 00:10:17.649
Sean: We're good.

124
00:10:17.684 --> 00:10:19.277
It's best that
everyone stays away.

125
00:10:19.319 --> 00:10:22.187
Ed: Whoever attacked us
won't stay hidden forever.

126
00:10:22.222 --> 00:10:23.087
Sean: I know.

127
00:10:23.123 --> 00:10:24.989
I'll speak to you soon.

128
00:10:25.024 --> 00:10:26.287
Ed: Take care. son.

129
00:10:32.899 --> 00:10:35.300
We will get through this.

130
00:11:01.027 --> 00:11:05.829
Billy: Dad's Big Bumper
Book of Rules About Killing.

131
00:11:05.865 --> 00:11:07.176
You look at that.
and you still just see

132
00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:09.135
a dead innocent kid. don't you?

133
00:11:17.911 --> 00:11:19.903
Sean: Billy's right.
This isn't working.

134
00:11:19.946 --> 00:11:22.916
Marian: What else
do you suggest?

135
00:11:22.949 --> 00:11:27.148
We had a killer in our house.
and I want to know why.

136
00:11:27.187 --> 00:11:29.418
You're the head of
the family. now. Sean.

137
00:11:29.455 --> 00:11:31.788
Keep doing what it takes.

138
00:11:39.299 --> 00:11:47.299
