139
00:11:58.017 --> 00:12:06.017
♪♪

140
00:12:07.260 --> 00:12:08.956
Vicky: Elliot.

141
00:12:08.995 --> 00:12:11.226
Where the fuck have you been?

142
00:12:11.264 --> 00:12:13.165
I have checked every
hospital in the city.

143
00:12:13.199 --> 00:12:16.192
praying I am not
gonna find a dead UC.

144
00:12:16.236 --> 00:12:18.102
You tell me next time.

145
00:12:18.137 --> 00:12:19.901
Elliot: I'm sorry.

146
00:12:19.939 --> 00:12:23.501
♪♪

147
00:12:23.743 --> 00:12:25.268
I've been holed up
with Shannon Dumani.

148
00:12:25.311 --> 00:12:26.142
They got me the best doctors.

149
00:12:26.179 --> 00:12:28.171
Don't worry. I'm good.

150
00:12:28.214 --> 00:12:30.445
Vicky: You still need a full
medical and a full psych.

151
00:12:30.483 --> 00:12:32.509
Elliot: I can't.
There's no time.

152
00:12:32.752 --> 00:12:34.243
Sean summoned me.

153
00:12:34.287 --> 00:12:35.798
He's spent the week hiding
out with his mum and Billy

154
00:12:35.822 --> 00:12:37.518
in a safe house.
just the three of them.

155
00:12:37.757 --> 00:12:39.157
Immediate family only.

156
00:12:39.192 --> 00:12:41.270
He doesn't know who tried
to kill him. or who to trust.

157
00:12:41.294 --> 00:12:43.263
but he trusts me.

158
00:12:43.296 --> 00:12:45.060
I took a bullet for him.

159
00:12:45.098 --> 00:12:46.430
I mean. a hired killer

160
00:12:46.466 --> 00:12:48.401
posing as a waitress
to get into their home...

161
00:12:48.434 --> 00:12:51.529
This isn't some
ordinary gang takeover.

162
00:12:51.771 --> 00:12:54.502
If the Wallaces want to survive.
they've got to figure it out.

163
00:12:54.540 --> 00:12:57.476
And I'll be next to
Sean when they do.

164
00:12:57.510 --> 00:13:00.173
I'll get you the names
and the connections.

165
00:13:00.213 --> 00:13:01.423
This could be about so much more

166
00:13:01.447 --> 00:13:03.279
than just taking
down the Wallaces.

167
00:13:06.552 --> 00:13:09.989
