this. they'll do it again.

168
00:13:12.225 --> 00:13:15.161
Alex: So. I wanted to talk this
through before going to Sean.

169
00:13:15.194 --> 00:13:16.492
Ed: Sure.

170
00:13:19.866 --> 00:13:21.410
Alex: I just don't think
it was a coincidence

171
00:13:21.434 --> 00:13:23.403
that Sean was attacked
when we were meeting Jevan

172
00:13:23.436 --> 00:13:24.904
and those investors.

173
00:13:26.873 --> 00:13:28.117
I think we need
to go to Jevan...

174
00:13:28.141 --> 00:13:31.168
Ed: No. Alex: Why not?

175
00:13:31.210 --> 00:13:33.145
Ed: Pointing fingers at
random strangers now

176
00:13:33.179 --> 00:13:34.306
will set Sean off.

177
00:13:34.347 --> 00:13:36.816
Alex: It's not random.

178
00:13:36.849 --> 00:13:38.327
Look. how about I go
to Jevan on my own?

179
00:13:38.351 --> 00:13:39.580
Ed: No.

180
00:13:41.187 --> 00:13:42.553
Alex: What are
you not telling me?

181
00:13:42.588 --> 00:13:45.990
Ed: The business that
you helped Finn build.

182
00:13:46.025 --> 00:13:48.256
the people that invested in it.

183
00:13:48.294 --> 00:13:49.956
they want you
to keep running it.

184
00:13:49.996 --> 00:13:51.807
Alex: Yeah. We're all agreed
on that... Sean included.

185
00:13:51.831 --> 00:13:54.494
Ed: They don't want
Sean anywhere near it.

186
00:13:54.534 --> 00:13:56.264
They want him gone.

187
00:13:56.302 --> 00:13:59.067
He's too noisy
and unpredictable.

188
00:13:59.105 --> 00:14:02.041
Alex: So. what?

189
00:14:02.075 --> 00:14:03.441
They tried to kill him?

190
00:14:03.476 --> 00:14:05.377
Our investors?

191
00:14:05.411 --> 00:14:08.404
Ed: They killed Finn.

192
00:14:08.448 --> 00:14:10.610
And they killed him because
he was trying to leave.

193
00:14:10.850 --> 00:14:18.850
♪♪

194
00:14:19.359 --> 00:14:22.056
Alex: How... How
long have you known?

195
00:14:22.095 --> 00:14:24.106
Ed: After Sean was attacked.
I went straight to Jevan.

196
00:14:24.130 --> 00:14:26.031
and got the truth out
of him. Alex: A week?

197
00:14:26.065 --> 00:14:28.159
Ed: I was trying to
think things through.

198
00:14:28.201 --> 00:14:30.261
trying to keep us
safe... Especially you.

199
00:14:30.303 --> 00:14:31.703
Alex: You do know
Sean's going crazy

200
00:14:31.871 --> 00:14:33.339
with not knowing
who attacked him?

201
00:14:33.373 --> 00:14:34.966
Was it the Albanians.
the Pakistanis.

202
00:14:35.007 --> 00:14:36.318
the Greeks. the
Kurds. the Chinese?

203
00:14:36.342 --> 00:14:38.402
Ed: Telling him now is
just going to start a war

204
00:14:38.444 --> 00:14:40.222
that we would never win.
Alex: I have to tell him.

205
00:14:40.246 --> 00:14:42.374
Ed: Think. We don't even
know who we're dealing with.

206
00:14:42.415 --> 00:14:43.625
Alex: Yeah. I do. I've
met some of them.

207
00:14:43.649 --> 00:14:45.345
Ed: You've met faces
who work for them.

208
00:14:45.385 --> 00:14:47.463
Alex: This is what you do.
You keep everything to yourself.

209
00:14:47.487 --> 00:14:48.864
so you can control
everything... Ed: Alex.

210
00:14:48.888 --> 00:14:50.220
Alex: and everyone around you.

211
00:14:50.256 --> 00:14:51.934
Ed: Alex. I am trying
to keep us all alive.

212
00:14:51.958 --> 00:14:53.324
Alex: Sean deserves to know.

213
00:14:53.359 --> 00:14:54.622
Ed: Listen!

214
00:14:57.563 --> 00:14:59.156
