243
00:18:23.202 --> 00:18:25.296
Elliot: Yeah. you
good? Billy: Yeah.

244
00:18:25.338 --> 00:18:26.338
Mm-hm.

245
00:18:26.572 --> 00:18:29.667
Come in. Elliot: Okay.

246
00:18:29.709 --> 00:18:31.405
