see sometimes.

249
00:18:39.318 --> 00:18:41.378
Yeah. happily married type.

250
00:18:41.420 --> 00:18:42.683
Suits me. though.

251
00:18:42.722 --> 00:18:45.590
I like the boundaries.

252
00:18:45.625 --> 00:18:48.288
Come on. Look.

253
00:18:48.327 --> 00:18:50.853
He's out of the country
for a few months.

254
00:18:50.896 --> 00:18:53.593
and we needed a
place to hide. so...

255
00:18:53.633 --> 00:18:56.262
We've got a few boltholes
like this round the city.

256
00:18:56.302 --> 00:18:57.702
