Yeah. rats. Look!

260
00:19:04.510 --> 00:19:07.480
Elliot: Whoa. mate. I
didn't take you for a baker.

261
00:19:07.513 --> 00:19:09.141
Billy: Well. I need
some kind of vice.

262
00:19:09.181 --> 00:19:10.672
Do you want one?
Have you had lunch?

263
00:19:10.716 --> 00:19:12.446
Have you eaten yet? Elliot: No.

